---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Get Started | Book a Plumber in Liverpool | Ideal Plumbing Solutions"
  description="Book a Gas Safe registered plumber in Liverpool. Free surveys for boiler installation, central heating and bathroom fitting. 24/7 emergency response. Call 0151 558 0334 or fill in our booking form."
  canonical="https://www.idealplumbingsolutions.co.uk/get-started"
>

  <style>
    .contact-page h2 { text-align: center; color: var(--navy); }
    .contact-page .section-sub { text-align: center; }

    .contact-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .contact-form-wrap {
      background: var(--white);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-top: 4px solid var(--orange);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 2rem;
    }
    .contact-form-wrap h3 { color: var(--navy); font-size: 1.3rem; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; text-align: center; }
    .contact-form-wrap p { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.9rem; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }

    .form-group { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.35rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .form-group label { font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--navy); }
    .form-group input,
    .form-group select,
    .form-group textarea {
      width: 100%; padding: 0.75rem 1rem; border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-sm); font-size: 0.95rem; font-family: inherit;
      color: var(--text); background: var(--bg); box-sizing: border-box; transition: border-color 0.2s;
    }
    .form-group input:focus,
    .form-group select:focus,
    .form-group textarea:focus { outline: none; border-color: var(--orange); background: var(--white); }
    .form-group textarea { resize: vertical; min-height: 120px; }
    .form-group select { cursor: pointer; }
    .form-note { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--muted); text-align: center; margin-top: 0.75rem; }

    .contact-info-wrap { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; }

    .contact-card-phone {
      background: var(--white);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-left: 4px solid var(--orange);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 1.5rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .contact-card-phone .label { font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--muted); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
    .contact-card-phone .number { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-size: 2.25rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--orange); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
    .contact-card-phone p { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.85rem; margin: 0 0 1rem; }

    .contact-card-email {
      background: var(--white);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-left: 4px solid var(--navy);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 1.5rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .contact-card-email .label { font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--muted); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
    .contact-card-email .email-addr { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--navy); line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
    .contact-card-email p { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.85rem; margin: 0 0 1rem; }

    .contact-card-coverage {
      background: #f8fafc;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 1.25rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .contact-card-coverage .label { font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--muted); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
    .contact-card-coverage .areas { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--navy); line-height: 1.3; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
    .contact-card-coverage p { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.83rem; margin: 0; }

    .trust-strip { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 0.5rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
    .trust-strip-item {
      background: var(--white);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
      padding: 0.85rem 1rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 0.6rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .trust-tick { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 900; color: #16a34a; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .trust-strip-item strong { display: block; color: var(--navy); font-size: 0.88rem; }
    .trust-strip-item span { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.78rem; }

    .urgency-bar {
      background: #fef2f2; border: 1px solid #fecaca; border-left: 4px solid #dc2626;
      border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; text-align: center;
    }
    .urgency-bar strong { color: #dc2626; display: block; font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 0.35rem; }
    .urgency-bar p { color: #dc2626; font-size: 0.9rem; margin: 0; }

    .contact-page a { color: var(--navy); font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(26,58,92,0.25); }
    .contact-page .btn { border-bottom: none; }
    .contact-page a:hover { border-color: var(--navy); }
  </style>

  <div class="contact-page">

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="page-hero" style="padding-bottom:1.5rem;">
    <div class="container" style="text-align:center;">
      <div class="page-hero-badge" style="margin:0 auto 1rem;">
        <span class="badge-dot"></span>
        Gas Safe Registered · 24/7 Available
      </div>
      <h1>Get Started with Ideal Plumbing Solutions</h1>
      <p class="page-hero-sub">Call us now for emergencies. Fill in the form below for free surveys, quotes and non-urgent bookings. We respond to all enquiries within 2 hours during business hours.</p>

      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:0.6rem;max-width:320px;margin:1.25rem auto 0;">
        <a href="tel:0151 558 0334" class="btn btn-orange btn-lg btn-full" style="box-shadow:0 4px 14px rgba(249,115,22,0.4);font-size:1.3rem;color:#ffffff;">CALL 0151 558 0334</a>
        <p style="color:var(--navy);font-size:0.82rem;margin:0;font-weight:600;">24/7 for emergencies · 7am to 7pm for enquiries</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- EMERGENCY BANNER -->
  <section style="background:var(--bg);padding:1.25rem 0;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="urgency-bar">
        <strong>Plumbing emergency? Do not use the form. Call us now.</strong>
        <p>Burst pipe, gas leak, boiler breakdown or flooding: call <a href="tel:0151 558 0334" style="color:#dc2626;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(220,38,38,0.3);">0151 558 0334</a> immediately. We respond 24/7 across Liverpool, Wirral, Warrington and St Helens. Gas emergency? Call Cadent Gas on 0800 111 999 first.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- MAIN CONTACT SECTION -->
  <section class="pf-section" style="background:var(--white);">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Book an Appointment or Free Survey</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">For free surveys, quotes and non-urgent bookings. We respond within 2 hours during business hours.</p>

      <div class="contact-grid">

        <!-- FORM -->
        <div class="contact-form-wrap">
          <h3>Send Us a Message</h3>
          <p>Fill in the form and we will be in touch to confirm your booking or survey date.</p>

          <div id="form-success" style="display:none;background:#f0fdf4;border:1px solid #bbf7d0;border-left:4px solid #16a34a;border-radius:var(--radius);padding:2rem;text-align:center;">
            <div style="font-size:2.5rem;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">✓</div>
            <strong style="display:block;color:#15803d;font-size:1.1rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Message sent successfully</strong>
            <p style="color:#166534;font-size:0.9rem;margin:0;">We will be in touch within 2 hours during business hours. For emergencies call <a href="tel:0151 558 0334" style="color:#15803d;font-weight:700;">0151 558 0334</a> directly.</p>
          </div>

          <form id="contact-form" action="https://api.web3forms.com/submit" method="POST">
            <input type="hidden" name="access_key" value="c36b8ee5-f01d-4b11-9d40-a2e5e5e16ffd" />
            <input type="hidden" name="subject" value="New Enquiry - Ideal Plumbing Solutions Website" />
            <input type="checkbox" name="botcheck" style="display:none;" />

            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="name">Your Name *</label>
              <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="e.g. Sarah Johnson" required />
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="phone">Phone Number *</label>
              <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" placeholder="e.g. 07700 900000" required />
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="email">Email Address</label>
              <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="e.g. sarah@email.com" />
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="service">Service Required *</label>
              <select id="service" name="service" required>
                <option value="" disabled selected>Select a service...</option>
                <option value="Emergency Plumber">Emergency Plumber</option>
                <option value="Boiler Installation">Boiler Installation - Free Survey</option>
                <option value="Boiler Service">Boiler Service</option>
                <option value="Gas Safety Certificate">Gas Safety Certificate (CP12)</option>
                <option value="Central Heating Installation">Central Heating Installation - Free Survey</option>
                <option value="Power Flushing">Power Flushing</option>
                <option value="Radiators">Radiator Installation or Upgrade</option>
                <option value="Bathroom Fitting">Bathroom Fitting - Free Survey</option>
                <option value="Hot Water Cylinder">Hot Water Cylinder - Free Survey</option>
                <option value="Shower Installation">Shower Installation</option>
                <option value="General Plumbing">General Plumbing</option>
                <option value="Other">Other - Please describe below</option>
              </select>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="postcode">Liverpool Postcode</label>
              <input type="text" id="postcode" name="postcode" placeholder="e.g. L17 6AB" />
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="message">Tell Us More</label>
              <textarea id="message" name="message" placeholder="Describe the work you need or any questions you have. Include any urgency, property type or specific requirements."></textarea>
            </div>

            <button type="submit" id="submit-btn" class="btn btn-orange btn-full" style="font-size:1.05rem;padding:0.9rem;color:#ffffff;">Send Enquiry</button>

            <p class="form-note">We respond to all enquiries within 2 hours during business hours. For emergencies call <a href="tel:0151 558 0334">0151 558 0334</a> directly.</p>
          </form>

          <script>
            document.getElementById('contact-form').addEventListener('submit', async function(e) {
              e.preventDefault();
              const btn = document.getElementById('submit-btn');
              btn.textContent = 'Sending...';
              btn.disabled = true;
              const data = new FormData(this);
              const response = await fetch('https://api.web3forms.com/submit', {
                method: 'POST',
                body: data
              });
              if (response.ok) {
                document.getElementById('contact-form').style.display = 'none';
                document.getElementById('form-success').style.display = 'block';
              } else {
                btn.textContent = 'Send Enquiry';
                btn.disabled = false;
                alert('Something went wrong. Please call us on 0151 558 0334 directly.');
              }
            });
          </script>
        </div>

        <!-- CONTACT INFO -->
        <div class="contact-info-wrap">

          <div class="contact-card-phone">
            <div class="label">Phone</div>
            <div class="number">0151 558 0334</div>
            <p>24/7 for emergencies. 7am to 7pm for general enquiries. A real person always answers.</p>
            <a href="tel:0151 558 0334" class="btn btn-orange btn-full" style="color:#ffffff;">Call Now</a>
          </div>

          <div class="contact-card-email">
            <div class="label">Email</div>
            <div class="email-addr">idealplumbingsolutions<br>@gmail.com</div>
            <p>For non-urgent enquiries, quotes and documentation requests. We respond within 2 hours during business hours.</p>
            <a href="mailto:idealplumbingsolutions@gmail.com" class="btn btn-full" style="background:var(--navy);color:#ffffff;">Send Email</a>
          </div>

          <div class="contact-card-coverage">
            <div class="label">Coverage</div>
            <div class="areas">Liverpool · Wirral<br>Warrington · St Helens</div>
            <p>All Liverpool postcodes L1 to L40. Plus the wider Merseyside area including Wirral, Warrington and St Helens.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="trust-strip">
            <div class="trust-strip-item">
              <span class="trust-tick">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Gas Safe Registered</strong>
                <span>Verify at gassaferegister.co.uk</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="trust-strip-item">
              <span class="trust-tick">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Our Own Engineers</strong>
                <span>No sub-contractors. Ever.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="trust-strip-item">
              <span class="trust-tick">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong>12-Month Guarantee</strong>
                <span>All workmanship guaranteed</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="trust-strip-item">
              <span class="trust-tick">✓</span>
              <div>
                <strong>250 Five-Star Reviews</strong>
                <span>Google · 5.0 rating</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT TO EXPECT -->
  <section class="pf-section" style="background:var(--bg);">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>What Happens After You Contact Us</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">We make the process as straightforward as possible. Here is exactly what to expect.</p>

      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:1rem;margin-top:1.5rem;">
        <div style="background:var(--white);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:1.25rem 1.5rem;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:1rem;">
          <div style="background:var(--orange);color:#ffffff;font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:900;font-size:1.25rem;min-width:2.25rem;height:2.25rem;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;">1</div>
          <div><strong style="display:block;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:0.2rem;">We respond within 2 hours</strong><p style="color:var(--muted);font-size:0.88rem;margin:0;">A real person calls or emails you back to understand your requirements and confirm availability. No automated responses.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div style="background:var(--white);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:1.25rem 1.5rem;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:1rem;">
          <div style="background:var(--orange);color:#ffffff;font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:900;font-size:1.25rem;min-width:2.25rem;height:2.25rem;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;">2</div>
          <div><strong style="display:block;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:0.2rem;">Free survey booked where applicable</strong><p style="color:var(--muted);font-size:0.88rem;margin:0;">For boiler installations, central heating, hot water cylinders and bathroom fitting we arrange a free site survey at a time that suits you. Simple jobs and servicing are booked directly.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div style="background:var(--white);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:1.25rem 1.5rem;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:1rem;">
          <div style="background:var(--orange);color:#ffffff;font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:900;font-size:1.25rem;min-width:2.25rem;height:2.25rem;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;">3</div>
          <div><strong style="display:block;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:0.2rem;">Written fixed-price quote provided</strong><p style="color:var(--muted);font-size:0.88rem;margin:0;">We provide a written fixed-price quote before any work begins. The price quoted is the price you pay. No surprises and no additions on the invoice.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div style="background:var(--white);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:1.25rem 1.5rem;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:1rem;">
          <div style="background:var(--orange);color:#ffffff;font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:900;font-size:1.25rem;min-width:2.25rem;height:2.25rem;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;">4</div>
          <div><strong style="display:block;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:0.2rem;">Work carried out to the highest standard</strong><p style="color:var(--muted);font-size:0.88rem;margin:0;">Our own Gas Safe registered engineers carry out all the work. No sub-contractors. Every job is covered by our 12-month workmanship guarantee.</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SERVICES QUICK LINKS -->
  <section class="pf-section" style="background:var(--white);">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Our Services</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Everything Liverpool homeowners and landlords need. All Gas Safe registered.</p>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:0.75rem;margin-top:1.5rem;">
        <a href="/gas-safety-certificate-liverpool" style="background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--border);border-left:3px solid var(--orange);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:1rem 1.25rem;text-decoration:none;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;">
          <div><strong style="display:block;color:var(--navy);font-size:0.95rem;">Gas Safety Certificates</strong><span style="color:var(--muted);font-size:0.83rem;">CP12 from £80. Same-day available. Combined with boiler service for £175.</span></div>
          <span style="color:var(--orange);font-weight:900;font-size:1.2rem;flex-shrink:0;margin-left:0.75rem;">→</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/boiler-installation-liverpool" style="background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--border);border-left:3px solid var(--orange);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:1rem 1.25rem;text-decoration:none;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;">
          <div><strong style="display:block;color:var(--navy);font-size:0.95rem;">Boiler Installation</strong><span style="color:var(--muted);font-size:0.83rem;">Worcester Bosch, Vaillant, Ideal, Baxi. From £1,800 fully fitted. Free survey.</span></div>
          <span style="color:var(--orange);font-weight:900;font-size:1.2rem;flex-shrink:0;margin-left:0.75rem;">→</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/boiler-service-liverpool" style="background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--border);border-left:3px solid var(--orange);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:1rem 1.25rem;text-decoration:none;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;">
          <div><strong style="display:block;color:var(--navy);font-size:0.95rem;">Boiler Service</strong><span style="color:var(--muted);font-size:0.83rem;">Annual boiler service £120. Benchmark updated. Certificate emailed same day.</span></div>
          <span style="color:var(--orange);font-weight:900;font-size:1.2rem;flex-shrink:0;margin-left:0.75rem;">→</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/central-heating-installation-liverpool" style="background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--border);border-left:3px solid var(--orange);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:1rem 1.25rem;text-decoration:none;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;">
          <div><strong style="display:block;color:var(--navy);font-size:0.95rem;">Central Heating</strong><span style="color:var(--muted);font-size:0.83rem;">Full systems from £3,500. Radiators from £200. Power flushing from £350.</span></div>
          <span style="color:var(--orange);font-weight:900;font-size:1.2rem;flex-shrink:0;margin-left:0.75rem;">→</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/power-flushing-liverpool" style="background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--border);border-left:3px solid var(--orange);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:1rem 1.25rem;text-decoration:none;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;">
          <div><strong style="display:block;color:var(--navy);font-size:0.95rem;">Power Flushing</strong><span style="color:var(--muted);font-size:0.83rem;">Cold radiators or noisy boiler? Power flush from £350.</span></div>
          <span style="color:var(--orange);font-weight:900;font-size:1.2rem;flex-shrink:0;margin-left:0.75rem;">→</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/bathroom-fitters-liverpool" style="background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--border);border-left:3px solid var(--orange);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:1rem 1.25rem;text-decoration:none;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;">
          <div><strong style="display:block;color:var(--navy);font-size:0.95rem;">Bathroom Fitting</strong><span style="color:var(--muted);font-size:0.83rem;">Full renovations from £2,500 labour. Plumbing and tiling included. Free survey.</span></div>
          <span style="color:var(--orange);font-weight:900;font-size:1.2rem;flex-shrink:0;margin-left:0.75rem;">→</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/hot-water-cylinders-liverpool" style="background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--border);border-left:3px solid var(--orange);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:1rem 1.25rem;text-decoration:none;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;">
          <div><strong style="display:block;color:var(--navy);font-size:0.95rem;">Hot Water Cylinders</strong><span style="color:var(--muted);font-size:0.83rem;">Vented from £600. Unvented mains pressure from £900. G3 qualified engineers.</span></div>
          <span style="color:var(--orange);font-weight:900;font-size:1.2rem;flex-shrink:0;margin-left:0.75rem;">→</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/showers-liverpool" style="background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--border);border-left:3px solid var(--orange);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:1rem 1.25rem;text-decoration:none;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;">
          <div><strong style="display:block;color:var(--navy);font-size:0.95rem;">Shower Installation</strong><span style="color:var(--muted);font-size:0.83rem;">Electric, mixer and digital showers from £200. Walk-in shower areas from £800.</span></div>
          <span style="color:var(--orange);font-weight:900;font-size:1.2rem;flex-shrink:0;margin-left:0.75rem;">→</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/" style="background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--border);border-left:3px solid #dc2626;border-radius:var(--radius);padding:1rem 1.25rem;text-decoration:none;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;">
          <div><strong style="display:block;color:var(--navy);font-size:0.95rem;">Emergency Plumber</strong><span style="color:var(--muted);font-size:0.83rem;">24/7 response. 30 minute arrival. Gas Safe. From £80 minimum charge.</span></div>
          <span style="color:#dc2626;font-weight:900;font-size:1.2rem;flex-shrink:0;margin-left:0.75rem;">→</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FINAL CTA -->
  <section class="final-cta">
    <div class="container" style="text-align:center">
      <h2 style="color:var(--white);font-size:clamp(1.75rem,4vw,2.5rem);margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Need Help Right Now?</h2>
